      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must have documented V&V test suite and version-controlled release process consistent with MRL 2 requirements.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022 R2 was used; the solver has a documented QA process including regression test suites and formal release notes. Version control and change management procedures are in place meeting MRL 2 requirements."
