      "acceptanceCriteria": "Code verification activities must demonstrate correct implementation of governing equations at MRL 2 level, including benchmark comparisons.",
      "rationale": "Benchmark problems including lid-driven cavity and pipe flow were used to verify correct numerical implementation. Results matched analytical solutions within expected truncation error bounds."
