      "rationale": "All five operating points (flow rate 2–6 L/min, rotational speed 2000–3500 RPM) were tested under controlled laboratory conditions. Temperature, fluid viscosity, and inlet/outlet pressures were recorded and directly applied as CFD boundary conditions."
