      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric between simulation outputs and experimental data must be defined and applied to primary QoI.",
      "rationale": "Relative hemolysis index (RH) was computed for all 5 operating points. Mean absolute error between CFD-predicted and experimentally measured RH was 8.4%, within the 15% acceptance threshold established for MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
