    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index comparison shows agreement within acceptance thresholds across all five operating points. Six factors were not assessed in accordance with MRL 2 scoping, which is acceptable per ASME V&V 40-2018.",
